00:54:32.070 --> 00:54:36.070
You too can become a bold and faithful preacher of the good news.

00:54:36.070 --> 00:54:37.070
How?

00:54:37.070 --> 00:54:42.070
By taking in Bible truths and building up strong faith in your heart.

00:54:42.070 --> 00:54:46.070
And then you'll be able to do like our sister did in the dramatization.

00:54:46.070 --> 00:54:48.070
Remember what she said?

00:54:48.070 --> 00:54:52.070
I had God's word in my heart and as a result,

00:54:52.070 --> 00:54:57.070
even in prison, when I was surrounded by all those difficulties,

00:54:57.070 --> 00:55:02.070
I did what I loved to do talk about God's kingdom.

00:55:02.070 --> 00:55:07.070
Another thing you can do is pray for more courage and faith.

00:55:07.070 --> 00:55:09.070
Remember what our sister said?

00:55:09.070 --> 00:55:13.070
It seemed that at times to speak up required more courage than I had.

00:55:13.070 --> 00:55:18.070
But not more courage than Jehovah could give me.

00:55:18.070 --> 00:55:25.070
So dear young ones, don't be afraid to talk about Jehovah and the truth

00:55:25.070 --> 00:55:31.070
to your schoolmates, to your unbelieving relatives, to your teachers.

00:55:31.070 --> 00:55:34.070
Good results will happen, for example.

00:55:34.070 --> 00:55:37.070
There is an experience of a schoolteacher here in the United States

00:55:37.070 --> 00:55:41.070
who had been searching for the basic questions as to the meaning of life,

00:55:41.070 --> 00:55:43.070
but she could not find them.

00:55:43.070 --> 00:55:48.070
But then her 12-year-old student at school asked the teacher three questions,

00:55:48.070 --> 00:55:50.070
the first question.

00:55:50.070 --> 00:55:52.070
Do you know I'm one of Jehovah's Witnesses?

00:55:52.070 --> 00:55:53.070
Yes.

00:55:53.070 --> 00:55:56.070
Would you like to learn more about Jehovah's Witnesses?

00:55:56.070 --> 00:55:58.070
Yes.

00:55:58.070 --> 00:55:59.070
Third question?

00:55:59.070 --> 00:56:01.070
Where do you live?

00:56:01.070 --> 00:56:05.070
Our 12-year-old sister started a study with her teacher.

00:56:05.070 --> 00:56:07.070
The teacher loved what she was hearing,

00:56:07.070 --> 00:56:11.070
made excellent progress and was baptized.

00:56:12.070 --> 00:56:15.070
That sister, the former schoolteacher,

00:56:15.070 --> 00:56:17.070
has been serving Jehovah now for many decades.

00:56:17.070 --> 00:56:20.070
In fact, for the last 40 years,

00:56:20.070 --> 00:56:24.070
she has been serving as a member of the United States Bethel family.

00:56:24.070 --> 00:56:29.070
So blessings come when we speak up and show strong faith.

00:56:29.070 --> 00:56:32.070
Remember in the case of the little Israelite girl,

00:56:32.070 --> 00:56:36.070
Naman would have never gone to Israel if she had not spoken up.

00:56:36.070 --> 00:56:39.070
And as a result, he was cured,

00:56:39.070 --> 00:56:42.070
but also became a servant of Jehovah.

00:56:42.070 --> 00:56:48.070
So in harmony with the strong faith of that captive Israelite girl,

00:56:48.070 --> 00:56:54.070
may Jehovah give all of us the courage we need to display our strong faith,

00:56:54.070 --> 00:57:00.449
even under the most stressful and even frightening circumstances.

00:57:00.449 --> 00:57:04.449
Brother Jeffrey Jackson will now consider the next talk of this symposium,

00:57:04.449 --> 00:57:17.739
imitate women of strong faith, Mary, the mother of Jesus.

00:57:17.739 --> 00:57:22.739
Jehovah chose the young woman Mary for a difficult assignment.

00:57:22.739 --> 00:57:28.739
It was a unique assignment, one that required great faith.

00:57:28.739 --> 00:57:36.739
It was to care for and raise the only begotten Son of God, Jesus Christ.

00:57:36.739 --> 00:57:40.739
What an amazing privilege that was.

00:57:41.739 --> 00:57:45.739
And yet it required strong faith on the part of Mary,

00:57:45.739 --> 00:57:49.739
not only because this was a very serious responsibility

00:57:49.739 --> 00:57:52.739
that would involve quite a number of years,

00:57:52.739 --> 00:57:57.739
but initially, Mary before accepting this assignment,

00:57:57.739 --> 00:57:59.739
had some concerns no doubt.

00:57:59.739 --> 00:58:04.739
One of them would have been the concern with regard to the reaction

00:58:04.739 --> 00:58:07.739
of her friends, neighbors, relatives,

00:58:07.739 --> 00:58:10.739
yes, of course, her fiance Joseph.

00:58:10.739 --> 00:58:14.739
After all, the angel didn't say to her, don't worry,

00:58:14.739 --> 00:58:18.739
I'll go and inform this of all the, to all the ones involved

00:58:18.739 --> 00:58:20.739
so that they don't get upset.

00:58:20.739 --> 00:58:26.739
So it was a very difficult and overwhelming assignment for Mary.

00:58:26.739 --> 00:58:29.739
Can you imagine how she approached this assignment?

